The Ott Tex Layout Package
==========================

1. Short Description
--------------------

This TeX package allows the users to adjust the way their Ott-generated rules
are displayed.

2. Manual
---------

To create the manual type "make" in this directory. This will create the
"manual.pdf", which contains lots of example uses of the package.

3. Authors
----------

The package and its manual were written by Rok Strnisa and Matthew Parkinson.

4. License
----------

The package is released under a New BSD License. See the package file
("ottlayout.sty") for details.